Package org.jgrapes.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Connection
    Represents an I/O connection.
    DataConnection
    Represents an I/O connection that is used to transfer data.
    NioHandler
    Defines the contract between a component using non blocking I/O and the NioDispatcher.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Extension
    Provides an extension of a channel for sending events downstream from a protocol converter component.
    File
    A component that reads from or writes to a file.
    NioDispatcher
    A helper component that provides the central hub for non blocking I/O components.
